overview.en: RRRating is committed to creating a decentralized, realistic, fair, open, and investor-focused, autonomous rating community. Help investors find value, avoid investment blind spots, popularize blockchain knowledge, promote the healthy development of blockchain ecology, and build a global digital asset tracking rating system.
overview.zh: RRRating致力于创建一个去中心化、求实、公正、公开透明、以投资者为核心的创新型的自治型评级社区。帮助投资者发现价值洼地，避免投资盲点，普及区块链知识，推动区块链生态的健康发展，构建全球数字资产的追踪评级体系。
